dc_title_s: Sectional map and a few convincing facts of Carlton County and vicinity
dc_description_s: Cartographic Details: Scale not given. "Lands in red for sale by Western Empire Land Co., Minneapolis, Minn." Covers the northeast portion of Carlton County, parts of St. Louis and Douglas Counties, and northwest Wisconsin. Panel title. Publication date not given on map but approximated based upon quotations in text from "Governor Johnson's Last Message" and of "Professor Thomas Shaw," presumably that of the University of Minnesota. Text on verso.|40 x 49 centimeters|Scale not given.|Minnesota County Maps, Plat Books, and Atlases
